    <scopecontent id="aspace_ad1a6862276d232b3635fae59d844d02">
      <head>Collection Overview</head>
      <p>Correspondence and personal and professional papers of Morriss and of his family (chiefly
        1848-1947). The material refers to the Civil War, medical administration in the Confederate
        Army, enslaved people, professional and family matters, and politics. Includes printed
        matter (mainly 1850-1875) concerned with politics and social reform.</p>
